--- title: Dahee Yun description: Interview for Dahee Yun --- Dahee Yun 윤다희 **Q: Name, year, major, UKA department/ position**
A: Dahee Yun, senior & masters, Corporate Communication/ Marketing, Operations Director
**Q: 이름, 학년, 전공, 유카 부서**
A: 윤다희, 4학년 & 대학원생, Corporate Communication/마케팅, 운영부
**Q: What is your favorite ice cream flavor?**
A: Cherry Jubilee
**Q: 가장 좋아하는 베라 (아이스크림) 맛은?**
A: 체리쥬빌레
**Q: When you were a child, what did you want to be when you grow up?**
A: An author… I wanted to write a book hehe
**Q: 어렸을 때, 커서 무엇이 되고 싶었는지?**
A: 작가… 책을 쓰고 싶었어 ㅎㅎ
**Q: If you were directing a movie, what genre would it be?**
A: Rom-com probably
**Q: 만약 영화를 연출한다면 어떤 장르의 영화일지?**
A: 로맨스 코미디 일 것 같아
**Q: How would you describe the color this color (teal) to someone who has never seen it before?**
![teal](../teal.png) A: Like dirty ocean water
**Q: 시각 장애인에게 ‘청록색’을 어떻게 설명할 것인지?**
A: 더러운 바닷물..?
**Q: If you were to become the president of UKA, what would be the first thing you would do?**
A: I think I would first plan for annual banquets.
**Q: 만약 내가 유카의 1인자가 된다면 가장 먼저 할 것은?**
A: 나는 제일 먼저 연례 연회를 계획할 것 같아.
